@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <!-- Link to Google Fonts for Roboto -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; /* Unified font to Roboto */
            background-color: #121212; /* Darker background */
            color: #f1f1f1; /* Light text color */
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 0 20px; /* General padding */
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #FF0000; /* YouTube red for the title */
            font-weight: bold; /* Bold title */
            border: 2px solid #FF0000; /* Outline in YouTube red */
            padding: 8px; /* Reduced padding */
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block; /* Make outline fit content */
            margin: 0 auto 15px auto; /* Center and space below the title */
            background-color: #282828; /* Slightly darker background */
        }

        h2 {
            color: #FF0000; /* YouTube red for subheadings */
            margin-top: 20px; /* Reduced top margin */
            text-align: center; /* Center subheadings */
            font-weight: bold; /* Bold subheadings */
        }

        p {
            margin: 10px 0; /* Consistent vertical margin */
            padding: 0 15px; /* Consistent padding */
            text-align: center; /* Center paragraphs */
            font-weight: normal;
            color: #e0e0e0; /* Light gray for better readability */
        }

        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff; /* Highlight color for main points */
        }

        .about-content {
            max-width: 900px; /* Set maximum width similar to Terms of Service */
            width: 100%; /* Responsive width */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center content */
            padding: 20px; /* Reduced padding for compact look */
            background-color: #282828; /* Dark gray background for the container */
            border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Dark shadow effect */
            text-align: center; /* Center all content inside the container */
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 0; /* Reset default padding */
            list-style: none; /* Remove bullets */
            text-align: left; /* Align text to left for list items */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center list */
            max-width: 600px; /* Set max-width for the list */
        }

        li {
            margin: 10px 0; /* Consistent margin for list items */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #282828; /* Dark gray background for the container */
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Dark shadow effect */
            text-align: center; /* Center all content inside the container */
        }
     
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="about-content">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our YouTube API project, a dynamic platform designed to provide seamless access to a wealth of YouTube video data. Our application leverages the <span class="highlight">YouTube Data API v3</span>, enabling users to search for videos, retrieve detailed video information, and filter content by various categories.</p>

        <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
        <p>Our goal is to enhance your experience by offering intuitive navigation and comprehensive filtering options, ensuring you can easily discover and enjoy your favorite videos, whether they are related to gaming, music, news, or educational content.</p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
       
        <ul>
            <li><span class="highlight">Advanced Search Functionality:</span> Quickly find videos based on keywords and categories.</li>
            <li><span class="highlight">Detailed Video Insights:</span> Access information such as view counts, upload dates, and channel details.</li>
            <li><span class="highlight">User-Friendly Interface:</span> Navigate through our app with ease, designed to resemble the familiar layout of YouTube.</li>
            <li><span class="highlight">Customizable Filters:</span> Refine your search results with category buttons tailored to your interests.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Thank You!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for visiting! We are excited to help you explore the vast world of YouTube content.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
